  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[IOS File System And CoreData]]></title>
    <link href="http://wear.github.com/blog/2012/02/19/ios-file-system-and-coredata/"/>
    <updated>2012-02-19T12:13:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://wear.github.com/blog/2012/02/19/ios-file-system-and-coredata</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>此篇文字用于记录学习IOS文件系统与CoreData的总结与笔记，以作备忘！</p>

<p>IOS把每个内部的文件系统是基于Unix的，不过做了文件保护，它把每个应用都放在一个独立的沙盒（sandbox）里面，应用只能访问操作自己沙盒里的文件。</p>

<h2>文件系统</h2>

<p>这个沙盒的目录包括应用程序包（Application bundle）目录，文档目录，缓存目录等目录组成。应用包目录是不可写的，文档目录类似MAC OS上的My Document，是操作文件的主要场所。其他的目录可以用　NSSearchPathDirectory　查找。</p>

<p>可用　NSFileManager　的</p>

<pre><code><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">-</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSArray</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="nl">URLsForDirectory:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSSearchPathDirectory</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">directory</span> <span class="c1">// see below</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nl">inDomains:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSSearchPathDomainMask</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">domainMask</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="c1">//NSUserDomainMask</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c1">// NSDocumentsDirectory, NSCachesDirectory, NSAutosavedInformationDirectory, etc.</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
</code></pre>

<p>得到相应的目录。注意返回是一个数组（历史原因），但通常只有一个地址。可以用如下代码</p>

<pre><code><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="p">[[[</span><span class="n">NSFileManager</span> <span class="n">defaultManager</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="nl">URLsForDirectory:</span><span class="n">NSDocumentDirectory</span> <span class="nl">inDomains:</span><span class="n">NSUserDomainMask</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="n">lastObject</span><span class="p">];</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
</code></pre>

<p>得到文件目录，</p>

<p>前面提到的　NSFileManager　为我们提高的许多操作文件的方法，比如检查文件是否存在，创建，复制，移动，删除文件，遍历目录等等。它是线程安全的。它的一些用法</p>

<pre><code><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">NSFileManager</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">manager</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[[</span><span class="n">NSFileManager</span> <span class="n">alloc</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="n">init</span><span class="p">];</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">-</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">BOOL</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="nl">createDirectoryAtPath:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSString</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">path</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nl">withIntermediateDirectories:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">BOOL</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">createIntermediates</span> <span class="nl">attributes:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSDictionary</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">attributes</span> <span class="c1">//permissions,etc.</span>
</span><span class='line'>                        <span class="nl">error:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSError</span> <span class="o">**</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">error</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">-</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">BOOL</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="nl">isReadableFileAtPath:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSString</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">path</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">-</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSArray</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="nl">contentsOfDirectoryAtPath:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSString</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">path</span> <span class="nl">error:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSError</span> <span class="o">**</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">error</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
</code></pre>

<p>NSString为我们提供一些用于生成地址的方便方法</p>

<pre><code><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
<span class='line-number'>12</span>
<span class='line-number'>13</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">-</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSString</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="nl">stringByAppendingPathComponent:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSString</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">component</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">-</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSString</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">stringByDeletingLastPathComponent</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">-</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">BOOL</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="nl">writeToFile:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSString</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">path</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nl">atomically:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">BOOL</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">flag</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nl">encoding:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSStringEncoding</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">encoding</span> <span class="c1">//e.g.ASCII,ISOLatin1,etc.</span>
</span><span class='line'>              <span class="nl">error:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSError</span> <span class="o">**</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">error</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">-</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSString</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="nl">stringWithContentsOfFile:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSString</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">path</span>
</span><span class='line'>                          <span class="nl">usedEncoding:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSStringEncoding</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">encoding</span>
</span><span class='line'>                                 <span class="nl">error:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSError</span> <span class="o">**</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">error</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">code</span><span class="o">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class="n">pre</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="err">　</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<h2>CoreData</h2>

<p>对应管理数据库的对象在CoreData里叫　UIManagedDocument，操作数据需要用到它的属性　NSManagedObjectContext。可以用如下方法创建 UIManagedDocument</p>

<pre><code><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">UIManagedDocument</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">document</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[[</span><span class="n">UIManagedDocument</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="nl">initWithFileURL:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">URL</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">url</span><span class="p">];</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
</code></pre>

<p>创建以后，你还必须创建或打开相应的数据库。首先，我们要检查有没有对应的数据库文件</p>

<pre><code><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'><span class="o">-</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="nl">openWithCompletionHandler:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">void</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="o">^</span><span class="p">)(</span><span class="kt">BOOL</span> <span class="n">success</span><span class="p">))</span><span class="n">completionHandler</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c1">// If it does not, create it using ...</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">-</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="nl">saveToURL:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSURL</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">url</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="err">￼</span> <span class="nl">forSaveOperation:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">UIDocumentSaveOperation</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">operation</span>
</span><span class='line'> <span class="nl">competionHandler:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">void</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="o">^</span><span class="p">)(</span><span class="kt">BOOL</span> <span class="n">success</span><span class="p">))</span><span class="n">completionHandler</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
</code></pre>

<p>此处用到了Block，因为CoreData读写不是线程安全的！完整的创建数据库连接的例子</p>

<pre><code><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
<span class='line-number'>12</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'><span class="n">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">document</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[[</span><span class="n">UIManagedDocument</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="nl">initWithFileURL:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">URL</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">url</span><span class="p">];</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="k">if</span> <span class="p">([[</span><span class="n">NSFileManager</span> <span class="n">defaultManager</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="nl">fileExistsAtPath:</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">url</span> <span class="n">path</span><span class="p">]])</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="p">[</span><span class="n">document</span> <span class="nl">openWithCompletionHandler:</span><span class="o">^</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">BOOL</span> <span class="n">success</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span><span class='line'>        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">success</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="n">self</span> <span class="n">documentIsReady</span><span class="p">];</span>
</span><span class='line'>        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n">success</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">NSLog</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="err">@“</span><span class="n">couldn</span><span class="err">’</span><span class="n">t</span> <span class="n">open</span> <span class="n">document</span> <span class="n">at</span> <span class="o">%</span><span class="err">@”</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">url</span><span class="p">);</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="p">}];</span> <span class="p">}</span> <span class="k">else</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="p">[</span><span class="n">document</span> <span class="nl">saveToURL:</span><span class="n">url</span> <span class="nl">forSaveOperation:</span><span class="n">UIDocumentSaveForCreating</span>
</span><span class='line'>      <span class="nl">completionHandler:</span><span class="o">^</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">BOOL</span> <span class="n">success</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span><span class='line'>        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">success</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="n">self</span> <span class="n">documentIsReady</span><span class="p">];</span>
</span><span class='line'>        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n">success</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">NSLog</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="err">@“</span><span class="n">couldn</span><span class="err">’</span><span class="n">t</span> <span class="n">create</span> <span class="n">document</span> <span class="n">at</span> <span class="o">%</span><span class="err">@”</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">url</span><span class="p">);</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="p">}];</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="p">}</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
</code></pre>

<p>创建后，你还不能立即使用它，你还必须先检查它的状态，必须确保它的状态是　documentIsReady，才能确保后续的读写操作正常。用如下的代码来检查</p>

<pre><code><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'><span class="k">if</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">document</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">documentState</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="n">UIDocumentStateNormal</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="n">NSManagedObjectContext</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">context</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">document</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">managedObjectContext</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="c1">// do something with the Core Data context</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="p">}</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c1">// orther states</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">UIDocumentStateClosed</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">not</span> <span class="n">opened</span> <span class="n">or</span> <span class="n">file</span> <span class="n">does</span> <span class="n">not</span> <span class="n">exist</span> <span class="n">yet</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">UIDocumentStateSavingError</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">success</span> <span class="n">will</span> <span class="n">be</span> <span class="n">NO</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">UIDocumentStateEditingDisabled</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">temporarily</span> <span class="n">unless</span> <span class="n">failed</span> <span class="n">to</span> <span class="n">revert</span> <span class="n">to</span> <span class="n">saved</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">UIDocumentStateInConflict</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">e</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">g</span><span class="p">.,</span> <span class="n">because</span> <span class="n">some</span> <span class="n">other</span> <span class="n">device</span> <span class="n">changed</span> <span class="n">it</span> <span class="n">via</span> <span class="n">iCloud</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
</code></pre>

<p>如果一些都正常，我们就可以正常使用了，用如下的代码保存数据</p>

<pre><code><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">document</span> <span class="nl">saveToURL:</span><span class="n">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">document</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">fileURL</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="nl">forSaveOperation:</span><span class="n">UIDocumentSaveForOverwriting</span>
</span><span class='line'>   <span class="nl">completionHandler:</span><span class="o">^</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">BOOL</span> <span class="n">success</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="k">if</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n">success</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">NSLog</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="err">@“</span><span class="n">failed</span> <span class="n">to</span> <span class="n">save</span> <span class="n">document</span> <span class="o">%</span><span class="err">@”</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">document</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">localizedName</span><span class="p">);</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="p">}];</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c1">// the document is not saved at this point in the code (only once the block above executes)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">Note</span> <span class="n">the</span> <span class="n">two</span> <span class="n">UIManagedDocument</span> <span class="n">properties</span> <span class="n">used</span> <span class="nl">above:</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="k">@property</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">nonatomic</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">strong</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">NSURL</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">fileURL</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="c1">// specified originally in initWithFileURL: </span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="k">@property</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">readonly</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">NSString</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">localizedName</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="c1">// only valid once associated with a file</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
</code></pre>

<p>当没有任何强指针指向 UIManagedDocument　之后，它会自动关闭。我们也可以这样关闭它</p>

<pre><code><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">document</span> <span class="nl">closeWithCompletionHandler:</span><span class="o">^</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">BOOL</span> <span class="n">success</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n">success</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">NSLog</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="err">@“</span><span class="n">failed</span> <span class="n">to</span> <span class="n">close</span> <span class="n">document</span> <span class="o">%</span><span class="err">@”</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">document</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">localizedName</span><span class="p">);</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="p">}];</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c1">// the document is not closed at this point in the code (only once the block above executes)</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
</code></pre>

<p>同时有多个UIManagedDocument实例是允许的，但注意有可能有冲突。有了UIManagedDocument实例之后，我们就可以用它的　NSManagedObjectContext　来操作数据了.
CoreData里对应数据叫做　NSManagedObject，类比Rails里的Active Model的一条Record，可以用　NSEntityDescription　类来操作它，比如保存</p>

<pre><code><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'><span class="n">NSManagedObject</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">photo</span> <span class="o">=</span><span class="err">　</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">NSEntityDescription</span> <span class="nl">insertNewObjectForEntityForName:</span><span class="err">@“</span><span class="n">Photo</span><span class="err">”　</span><span class="nl">inManagedObjectContext:</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSManagedObjectContext</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">context</span><span class="p">];</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
</code></pre>

<p>数据的字段就是它的属性，它遵守key/value coding协议，字段的值默认是nil,同时注意它所有的属性都是对象进行了对象封装，数据的写操作是先保存在内存里，你需要明确的指定保存。
我们可以利用Xcode的功能自动生产数据表的子类，这样就可用点来访问它的属性了。
删除数据</p>

<pre><code><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">document</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">managedObjectContext</span> <span class="nl">deleteObject:</span><span class="n">photo</span><span class="p">];</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
</code></pre>

<p>最后，我们来学习如何检索数据，这时候就要用　NSFetchRequest　了，使用它需要注意４点</p>

<ol>
<li>必须要制定要检索的表（Entity）</li>
<li>检索的条件，NSPredicate</li>
<li>排序　NSSortDescriptors</li>
<li>返回的数量</li>
</ol>


<p>一个创建NSFetchRequest的例子</p>

<pre><code><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'><span class="n">NSFetchRequest</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">request</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="n">NSFetchRequest</span> <span class="nl">fetchRequestWithEntityName:</span><span class="err">@“</span><span class="n">Photo</span><span class="err">”</span><span class="p">];</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">request</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">fetchBatchSize</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">20</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">request</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">fetchLimit</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">100</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">request</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">sortDescriptors</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="n">NSArray</span> <span class="nl">arrayWithObject:</span><span class="n">sortDescriptor</span><span class="p">];</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">request</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">predicate</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">...;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
</code></pre>

<p>我们可以制定一组排序条件，也可以自定义排序的方法</p>

<pre><code><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'><span class="n">NSSortDescriptor</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">sortDescriptor</span> <span class="o">=</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="p">[</span><span class="n">NSSortDescriptor</span> <span class="nl">sortDescriptorWithKey:</span><span class="err">@“</span><span class="n">thumbnailURL</span><span class="err">”</span>
</span><span class='line'>                                  <span class="nl">ascending:</span><span class="n">YES</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nl">selector:</span><span class="k">@selector</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nl">localizedCaseInsensitiveCompare:</span><span class="p">)];</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
</code></pre>

<p>指定NSPredicate范例如下</p>

<pre><code><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'><span class="n">NSString</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">serverName</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="err">@“</span><span class="n">flickr</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="err">”</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">NSPredicate</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">predicate</span> <span class="o">=</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="p">[</span><span class="n">NSPredicate</span> <span class="nl">predicateWithFormat:</span><span class="err">@“</span><span class="n">thumbnailURL</span> <span class="n">contains</span> <span class="o">%</span><span class="err">@”</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">serverName</span><span class="p">];</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c1">//更多例子</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="err">@“</span><span class="n">uniqueId</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="o">%</span><span class="err">@”</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="n">flickrInfo</span> <span class="nl">objectForKey:</span><span class="err">@“</span><span class="kt">id</span><span class="err">”</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="c1">// unique a photo in the database @“name contains[c] %@”, (NSString *) // matches name case insensitively</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="err">@“</span><span class="n">viewed</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">gt</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="o">%</span><span class="err">@”</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSDate</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1">// viewed is a Date attribute in the data mapping</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="err">@“</span><span class="n">whoTook</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">name</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="o">%</span><span class="err">@”</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSString</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1">// Photo search (by photographer’s name)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="err">@“</span><span class="n">any</span> <span class="n">photos</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">title</span> <span class="n">contains</span> <span class="o">%</span><span class="err">@”</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NSString</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1">// Photographer search (not a Photo search) Many more options. Look at the class documentation for NSPredicate.</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
</code></pre>

<p>也可以使用组合条件，甚至直接组合NSPredicate</p>

<pre><code><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'><span class="c1">//组合条件</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="err">@“</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">name</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="o">%</span><span class="err">@</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">OR</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">title</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="o">%</span><span class="err">@</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="err">”</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c1">//组合NSPredicate</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">NSArray</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">array</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="n">NSArray</span> <span class="nl">arrayWithObjects:</span><span class="n">predicate1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">predicate2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nb">nil</span><span class="p">];</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">NSPredicate</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">predicate</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="n">NSCompoundPredicate</span> <span class="nl">andPredicateWithSubpredicates:</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">];</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c1">// This predicate is “predicate1 AND predicate2”.</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c1">// “Or” predicate also available, of course.</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
</code></pre>

<p>一个更完整的例子</p>

<pre><code><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'><span class="c1">//Let’s say we want to query for all Photographers ...</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">NSFetchRequest</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">request</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="n">NSFetchRequest</span> <span class="nl">fetchRequestWithEntityName:</span><span class="err">@“</span><span class="n">Photographer</span><span class="err">”</span><span class="p">];</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c1">//... who have taken a photo in the last 24 hours ...</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">NSDate</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">yesterday</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="n">NSDate</span> <span class="nl">dateWithTimeIntervalSinceNow:</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">24</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="mi">60</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="mi">60</span><span class="p">];</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">request</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">predicate</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="n">NSPredicate</span> <span class="nl">predicateWithFormat:</span><span class="err">@“</span><span class="n">any</span> <span class="n">photos</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">uploadDate</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">gt</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="o">%</span><span class="err">@”</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">yesterday</span><span class="p">];</span> <span class="c1">//... sorted by the Photographer’s name ...</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">NSSortDescriptor</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">sortByName</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="n">NSSortDescriptor</span> <span class="nl">sortDescriptorWithKey:</span><span class="err">@“</span><span class="n">name</span><span class="err">”</span> <span class="nl">ascending:</span><span class="n">YES</span><span class="p">];</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">request</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">sortDescriptors</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="n">NSArray</span> <span class="nl">arrayWithObject:</span><span class="n">sortByName</span><span class="p">];</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
</code></pre>

<p>执行查询</p>

<pre><code><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'>    <span class="n">NSManagedObjectContext</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">moc</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">document</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">managedObjectContext</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="n">NSError</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">error</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="n">NSArray</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">photographers</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="n">moc</span> <span class="nl">executeFetchRequest:</span><span class="n">request</span> <span class="nl">error:</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">amp</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="n">error</span><span class="p">];</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
</code></pre>

<p>访问数据时，不能直接访问对象，只有直接你访问它的属性才能得到想要的结果。我猜是因为性能考虑！
CoreData的relationship是十分灵敏的，类似Active　Record，这里就不多介绍了.</p>
